author: rhuijben
msg: Avoid two to four DB transactions for every directory added by checkout,
update, merge. When just adding nodes we don't have to fetch pristine data
and we certainly don't have to perform actual property changes.
(close_directory): Add scratch pool variable. Only get and set properties
when that is really needed to avoid unneeded db transactions. Fetch
the properties from BASE to avoid issues with shadowing nodes.
